record.name: Docking Station
record.description: Provides desktop convenience with full port replication in a space saving design. Connect monitor, keyboard, mouse and other external devices such as the External MultiBay for ultimate convenience. Also includes support for Gigabit NIC pass through for Gigabit enabled notebooks.
